      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 20px; ">HTML Tag Reference</h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 30px;">W3Schools' tag reference contains additional information about these tags and their attributes.</p>
      
